Description: Functions for forming the likelihood-based
    confidence intervals (LBCIs) for parameters in
    structural equation modeling, introduced in
    Cheung and Pesigan (2023). Currently implements the
    algorithm illustrated by Pek and Wu (2018)
    <doi:10.1037/met0000163>, and supports the robust LBCI
    proposed by Falk (2018) <doi:10.1080/10705511.2017.1367254>.
